{"tid":1404459,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"街井與大廈的關係","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:54.000Z","uid":264281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f88f78ad1a89527f277b4e940acab03733644c","tid":1404459,"uid":264281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"圍住每棟building行一圈<br />\n你會發現地下有好多街井<br />\n井上面有會公司名 <br />\n以寬頻黎講 代表邊間電信商有線入去<br />\n（如果冇你用緊果間 代表佢租人地條線）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWKXzS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWKXzS2.jpg&h=f7cfff52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時無啦啦斷上網<br />\n就係附近有地鐵或者地盤施工<br />\n整斷左啲光纖<br />\n<br />\n咁斷左光纖會點呢？<br />\n成棟野上唔到網 <br />\n所以下次大家屋企又上唔到網既時候知道點解啦！<br />\n<br />\n當然街井下面仲有好多野<br />\n電線、電訊、排水渠、食水管、電訊光纖線、煤氣管等<br />\n<br />\n而香港最奇怪既地方係好多building 政府機構 軍事重地 啲街井都係任人開 呢點我就唔明喇 希望有高人出黎解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇下下面個blog<br />\n<a href=\"http://lausoldier.blogspot.com/2014/05/blog-post_25.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flausoldier.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F05%2Fblog-post_25.html%3Fm%3D1&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USPulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=52db7ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lausoldier.blogspot.com/2014/05/blog-post_25.html?m=1</a>"}]}